<template>

  <transition name="fade">
    <button snippet-menu-item
    @click="setView"
    :class="[
    'absolute',
    'transition-all duration-200',
    'p-3',
    'h-20 w-20',
    'opacity-80',
    'rounded-full',
    ]">
      <div
      class="w-full h-full rounded-100 hover:bg-white transition-all duration-1000"
      :style="{
        border: '1px solid ' + 'white',
      }"/>
    </button>
  </transition>

</template>

<script>

  export default {
    name: 'SnippetMenuItem',
    components: {
    },
    props: {
      viewName: String
    },
    data() {
      return {
      }
    },
    methods: {
      setView() {
        if (this.view !== this.viewName) {
          this.$store.commit('setView', this.viewName)
        }
        if (this.viewName === 'printout') {
          this.$store.commit('setView', 'print')
          setTimeout(()=>{
            window.print()
          }, 1000)
        }
      }
    },
    computed: {
      colors() {
        return this.$store.state.colors
      },
      view() {
        return this.$store.state.view
      }
    },

  }

</script>

<style lang="scss">

@media print {
  -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
}
</style>
